abstract: NBA Roundup; Toronto Raptors defeat Boston Celtics, 115-109; other NBA scores noted.
lead_paragraph: The Raptors won their season-high sixth straight game, 115-109, over the Boston Celtics on Wednesday night in Toronto.

headline.main: Raptors Defeat Celtics for Sixth Straight Win; Wizards Top Depleted Heat
